{"type":"text","timestamp":1781128840690,"sessionID":"ses_14c74eea9ffeIyeKUQdOD4vWgF","part":{"id":"prt_eb38d31fe001p0dzaaacKTiXVM","messageID":"msg_eb38d172a001mdI5nnm41J53Dz","sessionID":"ses_14c74eea9ffeIyeKUQdOD4vWgF","type":"text","text":"I found a concrete traceability/correctness candidate: Phase 009’s purpose says the BM25 resolver should help when exact matching is ambiguous and for `code_graph_context` seed suggestions, but the implemented query path only calls it after all exact subject matches miss. I’ll verify whether any context handler integration exists before recording it.","time":{"start":1781128835582,"end":1781128840688},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_0a32ae643b178ac8016a29de8398908191a68b6bed022144bd","phase":"commentary"}}}}
